<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٣٧ - <span class="c2">(٢٢٣٤)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4316">وَعُثْمَانُ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1132">جَرِيرٌ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ </a>- فِي هَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ بِمِثْلِهِ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>